POLARIS SEC CO said unconsolidated sales
in June fell 15.69% to NT$330,706,000 from NT$392,234,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  6/2011           6/2010
Sales            330,706          392,234    
YOY%             -15.69%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales           2,895,280        2,867,206   
YOY%              0.98%  
=================================================================
 